name: 2023 12th International Conference on Computer Technologies and Development (TechDev 2023)
content: Publication: Conference Proceedings: Submissions will be sent to at least two conference committee members for peer review. Accepted, registered, and presented papers will be published in conference proceedings, and submitted for abstracting and indexing by Ei Compendex, Scopus, etc. A few set of extended papers will be recommended to International Journal of Future Computer and Communication for peer review, and accepted papers will be published free of charge, which will be indexed by Crossref, Electronic Journals Library, INSPEC(IET), Google Scholar, EBSCO, etc.
